<ab facs="#facs_325_r1l31">hie beÿ vns cʒü <expan>Nur<ex>emberg</ex></expan> ſeÿ / . <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>f<ex>er</ex>ıa</expan> ṽ . <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> <expan>Bartholo<ex>m</ex>eȷ</expan> . </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_325" id="162r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
