<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan>, als wir ew nehst
                            <expan>geschrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> von <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> botschaft
                                <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>, daz wir die <add>czu</add>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>cziehe<ex>n</ex></expan> mainten, bis
                            <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> tag als nu auf Bartholomei ein end nem, in
                        des sind <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>
<expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> Meincze trefflich rete her czü uns kumen, von
                        den wir etwas gelernt <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, also daz uns wol
                        gevellet, daz ir ewr <expan>botsch<ex>aft</ex></expan>, die ir mit
                                <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>cze schicke<ex>n</ex></expan> maint, czü uns schicket, daz die <app><note><q type="date">auf
                            den <expan>nehst<ex>en</ex></expan> suntag</q>23.08.1411</note></app> cze nacht hie bey uns czü
                                <expan>Nur<ex>emberg</ex></expan> sey. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> v <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan>
<expan>Bartholo<ex>m</ex>ei</expan>.</ab>
